Package: latentClass
Type: Package
Title: Vanilla Latent Class Models
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2025-03-09
Author: Jannik H. Orzek
Maintainer: Jannik H. Orzek <jannik.orzek@mailbox.org>
Description: Provides a vanilla implementation of latent class models. The 
  objective is to allow for combinations of normally distributed and categorical
  variables as well as sample weights.
License: GPL (>= 3)
